Class TCreateTriggerStmt

  • java.lang.Object
    • gudusoft.gsqlparser.nodes.TParseTreeNode

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Visitable

    public class TCreateTriggerStmt
extends TStoredProcedureSqlStatement
    Create trigger statement. supported databases:
    • DB2
    • Hana
    • Greenplum, represented by TPlsqlCreateTrigger
    • Informix
    • MySQL
    • Openedge
    • Oracle, represented by TPlsqlCreateTrigger support dml, non-dml and database trigger.
    • PostgreSQL
    • SQL Server, support dml, ddl trigger
    • Sybase
    • Teradata
    See Also:
